{"tid":2217688,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新鴻基發律師信警告沙田區議員在商場設街站","createTime":"2020-09-25T15:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T16:21:01.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b209a00c13ede4c093423a409e54f4703fcacb5","tid":2217688,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200925-23_2OrjG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200925-23_2OrjG_1200x0.png&h=60af52f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田區議員趙柱幫今日（25日）發文表示，他因在沙田新城市廣場中庭設「12 手足中秋送暖」明信片街站，日前收到由新鴻基旗下私人公司「富棠置地有限公司」（Fu Tong Investment Company）及「啟勝管理服務有限公司」所出的律師信，警告其街站違反了新城市廣場的物業用途，不排除申請禁制令或賠償。趙柱幫表示，新城市廣場中庭一直是公眾活動的標誌地，但業主因無法向普通市民追究，便轉向追究有名有姓的區議員，認為行為是白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/120088031_2608011009529652_945603254759056073_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=25UmPkM1jmcAX-wRK0W&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=6551f015943d7abccd1213ae4d61ceda&amp;oe=5F943083\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F120088031_2608011009529652_945603254759056073_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D25UmPkM1jmcAX-wRK0W%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26tp%3D7%26oh%3D6551f015943d7abccd1213ae4d61ceda%26oe%3D5F943083&h=de9239b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/119990754_2608011029529650_3298920213902964835_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=09esgRbKilsAX8-tGiM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=f34b30def93093aeda9ac67bb3354366&amp;oe=5F9269B6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F119990754_2608011029529650_3298920213902964835_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D09esgRbKilsAX8-tGiM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26tp%3D7%26oh%3Df34b30def93093aeda9ac67bb3354366%26oe%3D5F9269B6&h=3ed99a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趙柱幫所收律師信由孖士打律師行（Mayer Brown）發出，信中指趙柱幫分別於 6 月 18 日、9 月 21 日及 9 月 23 日於沙田新城市廣場中庭擺街站，根據商場的批地文件，新城市廣場連接沙田地鐵站的空間只可作「步行通道」用途，在未經業主及管理公司同意下，大眾無權在中庭位置舉辦其他活動。<br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場業主及物管公司曾於 6 月 30 日就同類事件發信給趙柱幫，但趙於 9 月再設街站，信中要求趙柱幫立即停止類似行為，否則業主及物管公司或申請禁制令及賠償。<br />\n<br />\n趙柱幫向《立場新聞》表示，沙田新城市廣場中庭自去年反送中運動爆發後，便一直是公眾活動的標誌地方，但新鴻基禁止民眾設立「連儂柱」後，又兩次發律師信警告他不能再設街站，故意追究有名有姓的區議員，行為如同白色恐怖。他又指，中庭是有意義的公眾地方，故不傾向放棄在該地設街站，但將先諮詢律師意見再決定。<br />\n<br />\n趙柱幫 Facebook內 9 月 23 日的街站照片及帖文顯示，當日至少有十多名警員包圍街站，並警告現場已違反限聚令，要求市民立即離開否則作檢控，街站最後被迫終止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%AD%E8%A8%AD-12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%8E%E4%BF%A1%E7%89%87%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99-%E6%96%B0%E9%B4%BB%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BF%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E6%8C%87%E9%81%95%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94/?fbclid=IwAR3ftqT01OBl_9TkcE8B_p6fXiwd-KIcBoGPQPzi9v6YmdeWOo8XGCTxVSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%25A8%25AD-12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2580%2594%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ftqT01OBl_9TkcE8B_p6fXiwd-KIcBoGPQPzi9v6YmdeWOo8XGCTxVSA&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzgV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=1d7c62e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%25